    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Presented in exemplary showroom condition, this vehicle represents the pinnacle of automotive preservation. Every surface, from the flawless exterior finish to the pristine interior appointments, reflects a standard of care that exceeds even the most rigorous expectations. Mechanically unrivaled and aesthetically beyond reproach, this specimen offers a rare opportunity for the discerning enthusiast to acquire a truly investment-grade motorcar.",
