      "description": "Hey there! You have got to see this beauty. It\u2019s honestly in such incredible shape, you\u2019d think it just rolled off the showroom floor yesterday! I\u2019ve taken such good care of it\u2014not a single blemish and it runs like a dream. It's been my absolute pride and joy, and I'm looking for someone who will love it just as much as I have. Come take it for a spin, I promise you're going to fall in love!",
